Module: TFS Info

Displays information about items under version control.
Required Permissions
To use the info command, you must have the Read permission set to Allow for all specified files and folders.
Parameters:
Name Type Description
itemspec Array File(s) and folder(s) to get property of. If empty, equals CWD.
options Object Get command options
callback function Function to call back once executed
Version:
  • 1.4.1
Source:
  • tfs/info.js, line 5
